    <p>Idaho Department of Insurance (DOI) data for 2022 through 2025 shows non-renewal and premium increase complaints concentrated in Ada County (Boise foothills), Kootenai County (Coeur d'Alene area), and Bonner County (Sandpoint area). Idaho DOI does not publish detailed zip-code-level non-renewal rate data, but complaint patterns indicate where market stress is highest.</p>
